fr.umlv.wallj.game

Class Garbage

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.umlv.wallj.game.Garbage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Displayable, Cell

    public class Garbage
extends java.lang.Object
    Garbage is the element that the player must destroy to win. The DESTROY field is the constant telling that a garbage must be destroyed, and placed in Body.userData.
    Author:
    Severin Gosset - Denis Biguenet.
